message.body: Thank u so much for the clinic info! It was the best doctor/ medical experience I've ever had!
I know right! They're the best. Glad you got checked out. All good?
Got blood n urine tests. She thinks it's salt deficiency. Which cause bradycardia n leaky gut and now heat exhaustion. Whew! Life changes to be made! Thank u :)
Yea salt! Glad they (more than likely) figured it out. Now go eat some potato chips and get better! (Mindy n I are going to scratch night if yr feeling up to it...they have salty snacks!)
have rehearsal. What time u hanging till?
I am not going to rehearsal. My butt will not allow it, lol. Can't do too much or it'll come back :/
Tx! Hope I sees you soon!
